column11: Description
str
Patrol city streets and maintain peace in <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Limsa Lominsa</Case><Case(2)>Gridania</Case><Case(3)>Ul'dah</Case></Switch>.
Deliver written orders to unit stationed <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>at the De Nevelle Checkpoint</Case><Case(2)>at the Bannock</Case><Case(3)>at Sagolii Gate</Case></Switch>.
Patrol <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>middle La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the Central Shroud</Case><Case(3)>central Thanalan</Case></Switch> and eliminate potential threats to travelers.

<Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Group of kobold pickmen spotted in lower La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>Ixal raiding party spotted in the South Shroud</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa war party spotted in central Thanalan</Case></Switch>. Confirm presence of beastmen, and report current location. DO NOT ENGAGE.

Escort supply wagon to <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Camp Skull Valley</Case><Case(2)>Amarissaix's Spire</Case><Case(3)>Camp Drybone</Case></Switch>. Remain alert for possible threats, and ensure supplies arrive undamaged.

Residents of <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>middle La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the Central Shroud</Case><Case(3)>central Thanalan</Case></Switch> request military support. Deploy to area, and cull <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>goobbue</Case><Case(2)>treant</Case><Case(3)>giant tortoise</Case></Switch> population.

Cabal of minor voidsent spotted in vicinity of <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Woad Whisper Canyon</Case><Case(2)>Spirithold</Case><Case(3)>Nophica's Wells</Case></Switch>. Deploy to area and execute thorough “sweep and eliminate.”

<Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Camp Skull Valley</Case><Case(2)>Eugenia's Spire</Case><Case(3)>Little Ala Mhigo</Case></Switch> garrison requests reinforcements. Deploy to area and repel <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>kobold</Case><Case(2)>Ixali</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa</Case></Switch> assault.

High-ranking <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>serpent</Case><Case(2)>flame</Case><Case(3)>storm</Case></Switch> officer to visit city to plan Alliance strategies. Meet said officer at airship landing, and serve as personal guard for visit duration.
Patrol <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>eastern La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the South Shroud</Case><Case(3)>southern Thanalan</Case></Switch> and ensure major trade routes are secure.

Reconnoiter the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Kobold Dig</Case><Case(2)>Ixali logging grounds</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa encampment</Case></Switch> and assess enemy forces. Avoid engagements when possible, but mission completion takes priority.

Contact lost with unit deployed in enemy-controlled region of <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>outer La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the North Shroud</Case><Case(3)>northern Thanalan</Case></Switch>. Locate missing unit, and evacuate surviving members.

The <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Immortal Flames invite</Case><Case(2)>Maelstrom invites</Case><Case(3)>Order of the Twin Adder invites</Case></Switch> us to participate in allied maneuvers. Represent the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Maelstrom</Case><Case(2)>Order of the Twin Adder</Case><Case(3)>Immortal Flames</Case></Switch>, and uphold our company's reputation for excellence.

A joint operation is planned to prevent summoning of <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Titan</Case><Case(2)>Garuda</Case><Case(3)>Ifrit</Case></Switch> by forces entrenched in the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Kobold Dig</Case><Case(2)>Ixali logging grounds</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa encampment</Case></Switch>. Cooperate with allies to infiltrate stronghold and seize cache of ritual crystals.

A joint operation is planned to prevent summoning of <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Titan</Case><Case(2)>Garuda</Case><Case(3)>Ifrit</Case></Switch> by forces entrenched in the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Kobold Dig</Case><Case(2)>Ixali logging grounds</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa encampment</Case></Switch>. Cooperate with allies to infiltrate stronghold and seize cache of ritual crystals.
Rendezvous with Allied forces and join multi-pronged assault on <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>the U'Ghamaro Mines</Case><Case(2)>Natalan</Case><Case(3)>Zahar'ak</Case></Switch>.
Plans for sale of black market weapons uncovered by intelligence. Deploy to coordinates provided, and apprehend all involved in deal.
Reconnoiter <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Castrum Occidens</Case><Case(2)>Castrum Centri</Case><Case(3)>Castrum Meridianum</Case></Switch> garrison and report on enemy numbers and activity.

Man described as possible imperial deserter spotted in <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>eastern La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the East Shroud</Case><Case(3)>northern Thanalan</Case></Switch>. Locate suspect and bring in for interrogation.
Participate in allied mobilization against imperial forces in Mor Dhona. Ensure vital feint operation succeeds.

A large-scale operation is planned to disrupt <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Sahagin supply lines in western La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>Ixali supply lines in the North Shroud</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa supply lines in southern Thanalan</Case></Switch>. Deploy to area, and report to commanding officer for further orders.

Dangerous criminal wanted by the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Immortal Flames</Case><Case(2)>Maelstrom</Case><Case(3)>Order of the Twin Adder</Case></Switch> reported fleeing into <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the Black Shroud</Case><Case(3)>Thanalan</Case></Switch>. Coordinate with <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>flame</Case><Case(2)>storm</Case><Case(3)>serpent</Case></Switch> officer in charge of case and assist with pursuit.

Use imperial delivery schedule obtained by intelligence to locate and destroy Garlean supply wagon en route to <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Castrum Occidens</Case><Case(2)>Castrum Centri</Case><Case(3)>Castrum Meridianum</Case></Switch>.

<Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Minotaur of exceptional size</Case><Case(2)>Lamia in command of potent magicks</Case><Case(3)>Chimera of unprecedented savagery</Case></Switch> reported in local territory. Locate creature, and ensure threat is eliminated.

A joint operation is planned with the Scions of the Seventh Dawn to reconnoiter the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>kobold</Case><Case(2)>Ixal</Case><Case(3)>Amalj'aa</Case></Switch> for signs of summoning. Rendezvous with <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Slafswys</Case><Case(2)>Dariustel</Case><Case(3)>Alianne</Case></Switch> and do as our allies bid.
Training exercises are scheduled incorporating captured magitek weaponry. We are invited to participate and contribute to the development of counter-magitek tactics.

Civilians have been abducted by <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>the Serpent Reavers</Case><Case(2)>the Ixal</Case><Case(3)>the Flamefangs</Case></Switch>. Infiltrate the enemy stronghold and liberate the captives before they are turned into thralls.

Outlaws believed to be a splinter faction of the <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Mamool Ja</Case><Case(2)>Coeurlclaws</Case><Case(3)>Corpse Brigade</Case></Switch> have grown into an unacceptable threat. Find and summarily eliminate them.

The Lambs of Dalamud are engaging in illegal recruitment in <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>Limsa Lominsa</Case><Case(2)>Gridania</Case><Case(3)>Ul'dah</Case></Switch>. Under the guise of civilians, make contact with the cultists and bring their activities to light.

<Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>A succubus voidsent</Case><Case(2)>A troubadour voidsent</Case><Case(3)>The voidsent Anchag</Case></Switch> has been sighted nearby. Hunt down the menace before civilians can come to harm.
An abandoned suit of magitek armor has run amok. Hasten to the site and coordinate with the officer in charge to destroy the machine.
Brazen minions of the Illuminati are field-testing weaponry on sovereign soil. Confront them and put an end to the unsanctioned experiment.
A brutish man has been terrorizing citizens while masquerading as a serpent sergeant. For the honor of the Alliance, locate and apprehend the impostor.

Intelligence reports imperial sappers in <Switch(IntegerParameter(1))><Case(1)>eastern La Noscea</Case><Case(2)>the East Shroud</Case><Case(3)>northern Thanalan</Case></Switch>, en route to destroy city fortifications. Deploy to the area, and eliminate the enemy unit.
